- **Duration:** 1 Year  

This repository contains **weekly class outlines, notes, and code examples** for the Web & Mobile Development course.

The program starts with **HTML**, moves into **CSS**, then progresses to **JavaScript**, frontend frameworks, backend development, databases, and **mobile app development**.

